snippet.title: [GOTY 2018 #13] Best VGM 2252 - Tetris Effect - Connected ~ Yours Forever (The Deep)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS4
Tetris Effect (2018)
Connected ~ Yours Forever (The Deep)
Noboru Mutoh & Kate Brady
